message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you this great product. I think you'll really love it!
Hi Alice, $150 is a bit too high for me. I'm really interested in this product, but I can only go up to $85. What do you think?
I appreciate your interest in the product, Bob. I'm willing to meet you halfway, but I need to make a profit. How about $110?
Alice, $110 is still a bit high for me. I'm willing to go up to $95. This is my final offer.
I'm getting close to my minimum price, Bob. I'm willing to make one more concession. How about $105?
